channel.title: My Character Log
channel.description:
I'm posting this topic so I can log the achievements of my new pure (and for the enjoyment of showing off)
_____________________________________________________
Here's a real quick F.A.Q: _____________________________________________________
Q: What type of account is this?
A: A Turmoil Pure, I will explain this later
Q: Are you following a guide?
A: I sure am: http://services.runescape.com/m=forum/forums.ws?98,99,191,60698617
Q: When did you start this account?
A: Thursday the 1st (or 30th?) of july/june, if I recall correctly.
_____________________________________________________
Stats: _____________________________________________________
Attack: 40/60/70 - Strength: 43/60/99
Defense: 1/30 - Range: 56/60/70/99
Prayer: 11/43/95 - Magic: 33/55/94
Summoning: 1/41/99 - Hitpoints: 49/99
[center]Combat Level: 41[/center]
_____________________________________________________
Character Diary: Started July 5th, 2010 _____________________________________________________
Pre-Diary Achievements: 4 clue scrolls worth a total of 1.8M
July 5:
Range: 46 - 56 Clue scroll drop (40k Total worth)
July 6:
Range: 56-60 Strength: 43-45 Clue scroll (Had to drop because of a defense requirement) Woodcutting: 35-40 Slayer: 20-23 Hitpoints: 50-53 Strength: 45-50 Agility: 1-15 _____________________________________________________
Pictures: _____________________________________________________
My bank as of July 5th, not much :p
[img]http://j.imagehost.org/0825/bank_july_5.jpg[/img]
I will post more in the future :)
Thanks for reading!
